snippet: Cappelen had five birdies on the front nine on the way to a seven-under-par 65 that gave him a two-shot lead at the Sanderson Farms Championship in Jackson, Miss.
abstract: Sebastian Cappelen of Denmark takes a two-shot lead at the Sanderson Farms Championship in Jackson, Miss; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cappelen had five birdies on the front nine on the way to a seven-under-par 65 that gave him a two-shot lead at the Sanderson Farms Championship in Jackson, Miss.
